erkunft, Alter, Einziehungszeitpunkt und Überlebensdauer differenziert sind.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xCasualtiesvStatistics. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xCasualtieszGermany. 4aDeutsche Dienststelle. 4aMilitärgeschichte. 4aVermisste. 4aZweiter Weltkrieg. 70(DE-588)4135952-50(DE-627)1056612360(DE-576)209665084aQuelle2gnd 70(DE-588)4293571-40(DE-627)1041928360(DE-576)210953667aGefallener2gnd 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI0 cprintz978348620028740uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348659414040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486594140423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486594140/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014